# Skriber Frontend - API Status & Implementation Notes

**Last Updated:** December 12, 2025

---

## ‚ö†Ô∏è CURRENT BACKEND STATUS

All new recordings endpoints are now deployed and working:

- `POST /api/v1/meetings/launch`
- `GET /api/v1/recordings`
- `GET /api/v1/recordings/{recording_id}`
- `GET /api/v1/recordings/stats`
- `GET /api/v1/transcripts/{recording_id}`
- `DELETE /api/v1/recordings/{recording_id}`

---

## ‚úÖ WORKING ENDPOINTS

### Authentication (Working)
- `POST /api/v1/auth/register` - Register new user
- `POST /api/v1/auth/token` - Login (form-urlencoded)
- `GET /api/v1/auth/me` - Get current user
- `POST /api/v1/auth/refresh` - Refresh token
- `POST /api/v1/auth/change-password` - Change password
- `POST /api/v1/auth/forgot-password` - Request password reset
- `POST /api/v1/auth/reset-password` - Reset password with token
- `GET /api/v1/auth/google/login` - Google OAuth (NOT CONFIGURED)

### Meetings Launch (Working ‚úÖ)
- `POST /api/v1/meetings/launch` - Launch meeting recording(s)
  ```json
  Request: { "meetings": ["url1", "url2", ...], "duration_min": 60, "record": true }
  Response: { "created": [...], "count": 1, "db_status": "ok", "recordings": [...] }
  ```
  **Supports multiple meeting URLs in a single request!**

---

## ‚ùå NOT YET DEPLOYED (Returning 404)

For the recordings API, **none**. All of the endpoints listed above are now live and returning 2xx when called correctly.

---

## ‚ö†Ô∏è OLD ENDPOINTS (No Longer Working - 404)

These endpoints from the old API are returning 404:
- ‚ùå `POST /api/v1/meeting-bot/meeting-url` - REMOVED
- ‚ùå `GET /api/v1/meeting-bot/my-meetings` - REMOVED
- ‚ùå `POST /api/v1/meeting-bot/meeting/{id}/pause` - REMOVED
- ‚ùå `POST /api/v1/meeting-bot/meeting/{id}/resume` - REMOVED
- ‚ùå `POST /api/v1/meeting-bot/meeting/{id}/stop` - REMOVED

---

## ‚úÖ FRONTEND UPDATES COMPLETED

### 1. API Layer (`src/api/`)
- **types.ts** - Added new types:
  - `LaunchMeetingRequest`, `LaunchMeetingResponse`
  - `Recording`, `RecordingsListResponse`, `RecordingDetail`
  - `TranscriptSegment`, `TranscriptResponse`
  - `RecordingStats`, `RecordingsFilterParams`

- **meetings.ts** - Renamed to `recordingsApi` with new endpoints:
  - `launchMeeting()` - POST /api/v1/meetings/launch
  - `getRecordings()` - GET /api/v1/recordings (with filters)
  - `getRecording()` - GET /api/v1/recordings/{id}
  - `getTranscript()` - GET /api/v1/transcripts/{id}
  - `getStats()` - GET /api/v1/recordings/stats
  - `deleteRecording()` - DELETE /api/v1/recordings/{id}

### 2. Hooks (`src/hooks/useMeetings.ts`)
- `useRecordings()` - Fetch recordings list with filters
- `useRecording()` - Fetch single recording with polling for processing status
- `useTranscript()` - Fetch transcript data
- `useRecordingStats()` - Fetch stats
- `useLaunchMeeting()` - Launch new recording
- `useDeleteRecording()` - Delete recording
- Legacy aliases maintained for backward compatibility

### 3. Pages Updated
- **Dashboard.tsx** - Uses new stats API, shows processing recordings
- **Meetings.tsx** - Uses recordings list, date filters (client-side), delete action
- **MeetingDetail.tsx** - Renamed to RecordingDetail, shows video player & transcript
- **NewMeeting.tsx** - Uses launchMeeting hook

### 4. Routes (`App.tsx`)
- Added `/dashboard/recordings/:id` route

---

## üéØ FEATURES NOW AVAILABLE

1. ‚úÖ **Launch Recording** - Deploy bot to record meetings
2. ‚úÖ **List Recordings** - View all recordings with filters
3. ‚úÖ **Recording Detail** - View recording info, video, transcript
4. ‚úÖ **Video Playback** - HTML5 video player when video_url available
5. ‚úÖ **Transcript Display** - Show transcript segments with timestamps
6. ‚úÖ **Transcript Search** - Client-side search within transcript
7. ‚úÖ **Delete Recording** - Remove recordings
8. ‚úÖ **Statistics** - Dashboard shows total, completed, duration stats
9. ‚úÖ **Date Filtering** - Filter by today, week, month, custom range

---

## ‚ùå STILL MISSING / NOT WORKING

### Backend Issues
1. **Google OAuth** - Not configured on backend
2. **Pause/Resume/Stop** - Old endpoints removed, no replacement in new API

### Features Not Yet Available
1. **Transcript Export** - Need download endpoint with format options
2. **Video Download** - Direct download button (can use video_url for now)
3. **Meeting Sharing** - No share endpoints
4. **User Profile Update** - No PATCH /users/me endpoint
5. **Real-time Notifications** - No WebSocket support

---

